    <briefdescription>
<para>An ND builder that copies function values directly as interpolation coefficients. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>An ND extension of <ref refid="classIdentityInterpolationBuilder" kindref="compound">IdentityInterpolationBuilder</ref>. No computation is required because the interpolation coefficients equal the function values at the grid nodes (e.g. for an ND Lagrange interpolation on a tensor-product grid of nodes).</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>ExecSpace</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The Kokkos execution space. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>MemorySpace</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The Kokkos memory space. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>DataType</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The data type of field values and coefficients. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>IdxRangeInterpolation</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The ND index range for the interpolation mesh, of the form IdxRange&lt;Grid1, Grid2, ...&gt;. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>IdxRangeBasis</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The ND index range for the basis types, one per interpolation dimension, in the same order as the grids in IdxRangeInterpolation. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
